   {
    "titre": "Brown",
    "detail": "Brown the sausage rounds in a Dutch oven. Set aside."
   },
   {
    "titre": "Masala",
    "detail": "Sauté the onion, garlic, ginger, turmeric, and crushed chili together until fragrant."
   },
   {
    "titre": "Tomatoes",
    "detail": "Add the crushed tomatoes and let them break down into sauce."
   },
   {
    "titre": "Simmer",
    "detail": "Return the sausages and simmer for 20 minutes over low heat."
   },
   {
    "titre": "Serve",
    "detail": "Serve piping hot over white rice. CHEF'S TIP: crush the spices into a paste (the \"massalé\") before cooking them—they release far more aroma this way than as a powder sprinkled directly in."
   }
